Question_Text: What do you call 'productivity' that is actually avoidance?
What is your caffeine/nicotine signature? (What are you using to force-regulate your nervous system, and what does it cost you later?)
Where do you demand certainty that life cannot provide?
What does your mind 'assume will happen' before most investor or high-stakes meetings?
If you stopped trying to 'win' at work, what emotion would you be forced to feel?
Contraindications: Avoid if user is currently in an acute depressive episode; pace and provide grounding options.
